      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, i'll call them later, but it hurts so much right now and i don't want to wait hours for a callback. i've taken ibuprofen for headaches for years before i started the warfarin, it's usually fine. is there a reason why it wouldn't be okay just this once to take a couple of pills?",
